      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that's full of potential! This vehicle is in fair condition and is perfect for someone looking for a solid, functional car at a great price. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a reliable choice for your daily commutes or weekend errands. It's a fantastic opportunity to own a quality vehicle without the premium price tag!",
