    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but the suspension is beginning to feel a bit loose and there is a slow oil leak that will eventually need attention. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading on the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining on the carpets. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming maintenance tasks.",
      "price": 20000.0,
