      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained in absolute showroom condition. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a masterpiece of automotive engineering that has been preserved with exacting standards. Every surface, from the flawless coachwork to the immaculate interior cabin, remains in pristine, original state. This is an investment-grade offering that promises an uncompromised driving experience for the most discerning enthusiast.",
